      <t:profileDesc xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">
         <t:abstract>
            <t:p>General record for a not further identifiable collection of litanies.</t:p>
            <t:ab>Specific litanies that can be in the collection are e.g. <t:ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1806Litonz">Liṭon zaʾāryam</t:ref>, <t:ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1808Litonz">Liṭon za-śark</t:ref>, <t:ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4713Liton">Liṭon za-masqal</t:ref>,
               <t:ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3571Litonz">Liṭon za-maḫātǝwa fāsikā</t:ref>, the litanies of the week in <t:ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4860Litanies">Litanies for the days of the week</t:ref>, including
               <t:ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1807Litonz">Liṭon za-sanuy</t:ref>,
               <t:ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4858Litany">Sǝmǝka ḥǝyāw</t:ref>,
               <t:ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4266Litonz">Liṭon za-ʿārb</t:ref>,
               <t:ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4264Salota">Liṭon za-qadām</t:ref>,
               <t:ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4268Tazakkar">Liṭon za-ʾǝḥud</t:ref>,
               <t:ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4265Litonz">Liṭon za-ḫamus</t:ref>,
               <t:ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4859Litany">Wa-kāʿba nāstabaqqʷǝʿo la-ʾamlāka mǝḥrat</t:ref>,
               <t:ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7016Liton">Liṭon wa‐kāʿba nāstabaqqʷǝʿo la‐ʾƎgziʾabǝḥer ʾabuhu</t:ref>.
            </t:ab>
         </t:abstract>
